(lib/text/background)

The basic storyline as far as we know :P

     Everyone starts on the island. The island is ruled by pirates who regulate who and what go in an out of the island. No-one has been allowed to 
leave for decades and newcomers are placed on the island immediatly after 
being captured by the pirates. Your only option now is to live out your new
life on the island and hope that someday the gods will guides you out of 
this paradise prison into true freedom.

